title: Loudon Wainwright III - Complete Discography
description:
Well, this is it. This is as complete a discography as you are going to get without hunting down some obscure LP singles and ripping them, which I might well just do sometime, but for now this is complete enough, with every single album, as well as two exclusive single tracks from the "From hell to obscurity" cd.

I don&#039;t have the Rhino release of his first two albums, so I don&#039;t have the bonus track "The Drinking Song". While this song is, in a very similar version, on Album III, it is not the same, as I have heard a low quality mp3 of it. I ask, kindly, if anyone has this track to make it available.

I might do bootlegs later, if enough people are interested.

Cheers.
